data.description: Enjoy the views and quiet desert living in this highly sought-after community of Saddle Ridge! Stunning custom home built with luxury, style, and modern amenities throughout. Indoor, outdoor living is a seamless transition with glass doors, inside/outside surround sound speakers and fireplaces on both the patio and family room. Over an acre of space for a pool, RV garage, casita, etc., sky is the limit with this property!! Natural light pours in throughout the space to create an airy light feeling. The smooth natural wood plank tile gives the home a warm yet modern feel that makes it a great neutral palate for any décor. The kitchen has modern appliances, gorgeous granite counter tops and plenty of custom cabinets for storage The owner's ensuite contains a large tub, walk in shower, double sinks, and a huge walk-in closet. Truly exquisite home that is move-in ready!!
